flowchart TD
    A[TrainingData sau chuan bi] --> B[Auto Tuner phan tich du lieu<br/>samples, classes, imbalance,<br/>avg length, min samples]
    B --> C[Chon hyperparameters<br/>batch_size, epochs, learning_rate,<br/>max_seq_length, warmup_ratio]
    C --> D[Quyet dinh mode train<br/>fresh training hay fine-tuning]
    D --> E{Fine-tuning?}
    E -- Co --> F[Load model cu<br/>bat adapters + EWC]
    E -- Khong --> G[Khoi tao EnhancedPhoBERT moi]
    F --> H[Train/val split stratified]
    G --> H
    H --> I[ClassBalancedBatchSampler<br/>neu bat contrastive learning]
    I --> J[Train loop<br/>optimizer AdamW + scheduler]
    J --> K[Loss tong hop<br/>classification + contrastive + EWC]
    K --> L[FP16 + gradient accumulation<br/>clip grad + OOM auto-retry]
    L --> M[Danh gia val accuracy moi epoch]
    M --> N{Con cai thien?}
    N -- Co --> O[Luu best checkpoint]
    N -- Khong --> P[Dem patience]
    P --> Q{Dat early stopping?}
    Q -- Chua --> J
    Q -- Roi --> R[Restore best model]
    O --> J
    R --> S[Temperature scaling tren val set]
    S --> T[Tinh class centroids cho OOD]
    T --> U[Persist weights, config,<br/>intent_ids, training_data]
